annotations.title: Viewer Cocktail: Spring Swing

textContent:
2oz St. George botanivore gin
0.5oz simple syrup
0.75oz lemon juice 
0.5oz luxardo maraschino liquor
0.5oz St Germain (elderflower liquor)
3 cucumber wheels
2 strawberry slices

Pour ingredients into shaker, muddle, then shake. Double strain into coupe glass. Garnish with strawberry slice and cucumber wheel.
